{"tid":1639240,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有咩笑話好笑得過支那人話自己唔係玻璃心？歡迎列舉","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T14:40:47.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54b02c98e13bc9d3dc9656fe111c7e56dd4e718c","tid":1639240,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/9aLQKM6.png\" /><br />\n警察：我唔係狗<br />\n林鄭：我冇出賣香港人"},{"pid":"47a82789e2a8873299a0829d04eb83a96f75b45b","tid":1639240,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/9aLQKM6.png\" /><br />\n中國空氣很新鮮<br />\n六四冇死人<br />\n習近平唔係維尼熊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據報導，美國商務部發佈公告，將中國維吾爾自治區新疆維吾爾自治區公安廳及其18家下屬機構，還有新疆生產建設兵團公安局、海康威視等8家中國企業列入出口管制實體清單。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人耿爽回應稱，美方以所謂人權問題為藉口，把中國新疆維吾爾自治區公安廳、新疆生產建設兵團公安局等機構，以及8家中國企業列入管制實體清單，實施出口限制。這種行徑嚴重的違反了國際關係基本準則，干涉中國內政，損害中方利益，中方對此表示強烈不滿和堅決反對。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽強調，新疆事務純屬中國內政，任何國家無權干涉。新疆根本不存在美方所稱的所謂的人權問題，有關指責不過是美方為干涉中國內政蓄意製造的藉口。新疆採取的反恐和去極端化舉措，目的是從源頭上預防極端主義和恐怖主義的滋生，完全符合中國法律，也符合國際實踐，這些舉措受到2500萬新疆各族人民的廣泛支持，也為國際反恐事業作出了積極貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽指出，美方對中方的指責完全是顛倒黑白，一派胡言，只能進一步暴露其干擾新疆反恐努力，阻撓中國穩定發展的險惡用心。中方敦促美方立即糾正錯誤，撤銷有關決定，中方將繼續堅決維護國家主權安全和發展利益。"},{"pid":"e381f9e5f62cc505782d90c8cf8bb436ba91700c","tid":1639240,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71940180_3421918924515372_3971722972061761536_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmWHswJapVla5jnRLDo2UV3BYFUOwqMNHIsUky5syqL9WNv7Hr0UEBEzuLenDp_xQQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=f3c2bea7c75c5a8cafa208d6b0d428c6&amp;oe=5E1C1037\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71940180_3421918924515372_3971722972061761536_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmWHswJapVla5jnRLDo2UV3BYFUOwqMNHIsUky5syqL9WNv7Hr0UEBEzuLenDp_xQQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Df3c2bea7c75c5a8cafa208d6b0d428c6%26oe%3D5E1C1037&h=e2daaded&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"275cdf914b153b977246dbed1bbd5dcc0e2049e9","tid":1639240,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"中國人權全世界最好"},{"pid":"b39c4499b2d1a60b80433d0843802c41fbf0b433","tid":1639240,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:36:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係豆腐心呀</span>"},{"pid":"9f6d5361c5c2e1831e64d7aec969e5f29b623d35","tid":1639240,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"中國內政不容外國勢力說三道四<br />\n強烈譴責美國通過香港民主人權法案<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fede5c58f0c5e711e07733d6369f81437971772","tid":1639240,"uid":143230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47a82789e2a8873299a0829d04eb83a96f75b45b","tid":1639240,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/9aLQKM6.png\